OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What help and
OL,4,Csupport is available?
OL,6,FTens of thousands of people in the UK
OL,7,Fwere infected with HIV and/or
OL,8,Fhepatitis after they were given
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood and blood products
OL,10,Fbetween the 1970s and early 1990s.
OL,12,FThe , the inquiry into the disaster
OL,13,Fconcluded.
OL,15,FLabelled the "worst treatment disaster
OL,16,Fin the NHS," the saw more than 30,000
OL,17,Fpeople infected with HIV and Hepatitis
OL,18,FC after being treated with
OL,19,Fcontaminated blood products.
