OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What help and
OL,4,Csupport is available?
OL,6,FThese include people who needed blood
OL,7,Ftransfusions for accidents, in surgery
OL,8,For during childbirth, and patients
OL,9,Fwith certain blood disorders who were
OL,10,Ftreated with donated blood plasma or
OL,11,Fblood transfusions.
OL,13,FReport author Sir Brian Langstaff
OL,14,Fconcluded "the chief responsibility
OL,15,Ffor the failings lied with successive
OL,16,Fgovernments", and that they "showed
OL,17,Flittle interest in finding the truth".
OL,19,FWill infected blood scandal victims
OL,20,Fget compensation?
