OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What help and
OL,4,Csupport is available?
OL,6,FThe government is now working at pace
OL,7,Fto get an arms-length compensation
OL,8,Fbody set up, having faced criticism in
OL,9,Fthe past over the speed at which it
OL,10,Fresponded to calls for action on
OL,11,Fcompensation.
OL,13,FInterim compensation payments of
OL,14,F#100,000 have been made to around
OL,15,F4,000 infected people or bereaved
OL,16,Fpartners, following advice from the
OL,17,Finquiry.
