OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What help and
OL,4,Csupport is available?
OL,6,FMinisters recently announced that
OL,7,Fthese interim payments would be
OL,8,Fextended to the "estates of the
OL,9,Fdeceased".
OL,11,FIn April 2023, Sir Brian said interim
OL,12,Fcompensation should also be offered to
OL,13,Fthe children and parents of those
OL,14,Finfected.
OL,16,FHe also recommended a final
OL,17,Fcompensation scheme be set up. The
OL,18,Ftotal cost is likely to run into
OL,19,Fbillions.
