OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What help and
OL,4,Csupport is available?
OL,6,FThe government has said it accepts the
OL,7,Fcase for compensation but it would be
OL,8,F"inappropriate" to respond before the
OL,9,Finquiry's full report.
OL,11,FIn April 2024, ministers agreed to
OL,12,Fsupport a Labour amendment to the
OL,13,FVictims and Prisoners Bill.
OL,15,FIt means a final compensation scheme
OL,16,Fmust be set up within three months of
OL,17,Fthe legislation becoming law.
