OL,11,FWhat help and support is available to
OL,12,Fthose affected?
OL,14,FThe UK government make support
OL,15,Fpayments to people who contracted
OL,16,FHepatitis C via an NHS blood
OL,17,Ftransfusion or blood products before
OL,18,FSeptember 1991.
